  "prompt": "What is best steakhouse in San Diego?",
  "response": "San Diego has a variety of excellent steakhouses, each with its own unique atmosphere, menu, and specialties. Here are some of the top-rated steakhouses in the area:\n\n1. **Cowboy Star Restaurant & Butcher Shop**  \n   Located in the East Village, Cowboy Star is known for its high-quality, sustainably sourced meats and a sophisticated yet rustic ambiance. It\u2019s a great choice for classic steakhouse dishes with a modern twist.\n\n2. **Donovan\u2019s Steak & Chop House**  \n   With locations in La Jolla and downtown San Diego, Donovan\u2019s is a local favorite for its elegant setting, exceptional service, and perfectly cooked steaks. Their wine list is also impressive.\n\n3. **Fleming\u2019s Prime Steakhouse & Wine Bar**  \n   Situated in the Gaslamp Quarter, Fleming\u2019s offers a refined dining experience with a focus on prime cuts of beef and an extensive wine selection. Their sides and desserts are also highly praised.\n\n4. **Ruth\u2019s Chris Steak House**  \n   Located in the heart of downtown, Ruth\u2019s Chris is a classic steakhouse chain known for its sizzling steaks served on 500-degree plates. It\u2019s a reliable choice for a luxurious steak dinner.\n\n5. **Born & Raised**  \n   This modern steakhouse in Little Italy is known for its upscale, Art Deco-inspired design and premium cuts of meat, including Wagyu and dry-aged options. It\u2019s a trendy spot with a lively bar scene.\n\n6. **STK Steakhouse**  \n   Situated in the Gaslamp Quarter, STK offers a chic, contemporary vibe with a focus on steaks, seafood, and craft cocktails. It\u2019s a great spot for a night out with a more energetic atmosphere.\n\n7. **The Butcher\u2019s Cut**  \n   Located in the Pendry San Diego hotel, this upscale steakhouse offers a blend of classic and innovative dishes, with a focus on prime cuts and house-made charcuterie.\n\nThe \"best\" steakhouse depends on your preferences for ambiance, style, and specific cuts of meat. Each of these options offers a fantastic dining experience, so you can\u2019t go wrong!",
